WEBVTT

00:00:00.585 --> 00:00:02.452
her AVRAHAM Sherman

00:00:04.315 --> 00:00:08.747
mir geyen foroys mit undzer intervyu, kasete numer s- zeks

00:00:09.192 --> 00:00:16.870
kh'hob aykh gevolt nokh fregn a frage, tsi iz epes vos ikh hob nisht gefregt ⟨ober zikh⟩ dermant ir hot gevolt nokh epes tsugebn tsu ayer

00:00:16.870 --> 00:00:17.927
SIPUR?

00:00:18.338 --> 00:00:19.918
tsugebn

00:00:20.295 --> 00:00:25.857
ikh zol veln dertseyln di zakhn d- nokh andere zakhn UNK dos iz, s'hot nisht, s'hot nisht keyn shier.

00:00:26.033 --> 00:00:28.406
me ken dertseyln un dertseyln un dertseyln.

00:00:28.429 --> 00:00:34.025
ikh vil aykh nokh dertseyln an ⟨epizodn⟩ in vos, ikh vel dos keyn mol nisht fargesn. in BUCHENWALD dos hot pasirt.

00:00:35.331 --> 00:00:39.192
s'iz take haynt lekherlekh aza zakh, ober demolt iz gevezn a

00:00:39.192 --> 00:00:40.860
a frage fun lebn un toyt.

00:00:41.895 --> 00:00:47.052
m'hot undz gegebn yedn tog in BUCHENWALD hot men undz gegebn aza min ⟨MONETA⟩ hot dos geheysn, aza min

00:00:47.413 --> 00:00:48.470
fun blekh.

00:00:48.595 --> 00:00:51.457
mit dem zenen mir araynganen un m'hot gekrign a

00:00:51.717 --> 00:00:53.095
a shtikl broyt

00:00:53.758 --> 00:00:55.389
a tsentl fun a breytl

00:00:55.412 --> 00:00:57.600
un a lefl zup.

00:00:58.618 --> 00:01:02.611
un shteyendik azoy in di reye hot men nebekh bay mayn tatn aroysgeganvet dos

00:01:03.681 --> 00:01:06.459
un mir beyde hobn zikh gemuzt teyln mit undzer

00:01:06.651 --> 00:01:09.986
dos iz demolt gevezn aza tragedye. s'iz haynt efsher nisht

00:01:09.992 --> 00:01:11.555
zet oys lekherlekh

00:01:11.848 --> 00:01:14.170
ober ikh ken dos key- ikh ken dos nisht fargesn

00:01:15.477 --> 00:01:17.310
az ikh hob badorfn avekgebn

00:01:17.755 --> 00:01:20.415
hob badorfn avekgebn dem tatn a halbn fun mayn

00:01:21.096 --> 00:01:22.473
fun mayn portsye.

00:01:23.374 --> 00:01:24.363
es iz

00:01:24.589 --> 00:01:26.591
dos, dos gedenk ikh eyn zakh.

00:01:26.665 --> 00:01:29.578
s'iz do epizodn

00:01:29.736 --> 00:01:30.641
dos iz

00:01:30.681 --> 00:01:33.358
ken dertseyln epizodn on a shier, ober s-

00:01:34.225 --> 00:01:36.463
veys nisht bay velekhn ontsuheybn ⟨vayl s'iz shoyn⟩.

00:01:38.832 --> 00:01:42.285
s'iz yeder, tsum baysh- kimat yedn tog iz gevezn a

00:01:44.012 --> 00:01:47.752
an iberlebenish. yedn tog iz geven an ander iberlebenish

00:01:47.826 --> 00:01:50.202
in lager. s'iz gev- s'iz geven azelekhene zakhn

00:01:50.202 --> 00:01:52.781
tsum bayshpil, der mentsh aleyn iz gevorn mamesh

00:01:53.142 --> 00:01:55.363
azoy apatish, azoy glaykhgiltik

00:01:55.605 --> 00:01:57.826
az s'hot im gornisht onge- bloyz

00:01:58.120 --> 00:02:00.023
der instinkt fun a khaye

00:02:00.023 --> 00:02:01.303
bloyz tsu ekzistirn.

00:02:02.389 --> 00:02:04.340
m'hot nisht gekler- m'hot nisht ge-

00:02:04.465 --> 00:02:06.638
der tsveyter hot nisht gehat keyn shum BEDEUTUNG.

00:02:06.638 --> 00:02:07.749
der tsveyter perzon.

00:02:10.388 --> 00:02:14.297
ir hot mir dertseylt frier az ir hot got tsu danken akht eyniklekh.

00:02:15.838 --> 00:02:20.725
az ir treft zikh mit zey, fregn zey, interesirn zey zikh a bisl? oykh nisht?

00:02:19.850 --> 00:02:22.770
iber hoypt nisht. di eyniklekh iber hoypt nisht.

00:02:24.310 --> 00:02:28.742
yetst, az mayn eyni- eyner fun mayne eyniklekh hot badorfn makhn epes a

00:02:28.866 --> 00:02:30.736
a shtikl arbet far di shule

00:02:30.736 --> 00:02:32.685
hot mikh mayn tokhter ongerufn

00:02:32.685 --> 00:02:36.144
davke nisht fun lager nor fun di, fun di familye.

00:02:36.144 --> 00:02:38.631
⟨afile⟩ fun di familye veysn zey zeyer veynik.

00:02:40.476 --> 00:02:41.550
dos iz

00:02:42.855 --> 00:02:44.679
ikh hob gevolt

00:02:44.679 --> 00:02:45.999
danken

00:02:45.999 --> 00:02:48.989
far dem onshtrengung vos ir hot gemakht biz yetst

00:02:48.989 --> 00:02:51.529
un bald veln mir aribergeyn

00:02:51.529 --> 00:02:55.759
tsu der teyl ven me vet aykh nemen a foto tsuzamen mit ayer froy.

00:02:55.759 --> 00:02:57.040
mit ayer erloybenish.

00:03:04.747 --> 00:03:07.295
⟨ikh vel⟩ forshteln mayn froy, FRIDA

00:03:07.295 --> 00:03:09.208
fun di heym Dine.

00:04:24.527 --> 00:04:26.751
a sheynem dank. SPASIBO BOL'SHOYE

00:04:34.213 --> 00:04:35.550
dos iz

00:04:35.550 --> 00:04:38.882
a bild fun mayne eltern, mayn foter un mayn muter.

00:04:38.882 --> 00:04:40.882
der foter Yitskhok Sherman

00:04:40.882 --> 00:04:43.582
di muter Khaye, fun der heym TEITELBAUM.

00:04:44.302 --> 00:04:46.100
dos bild

00:04:46.100 --> 00:04:48.490
ikh ken nisht genoy gedenken

00:04:48.490 --> 00:04:52.040
tsi dos iz far di khasene oder nokh di khasene.

00:04:52.040 --> 00:04:56.040
ober ikh shtel dos for az dos bild muz zayn bay zeks, zibn un zibetsik yor alt.

00:04:57.300 --> 00:05:00.000
un der tate iz nebekh ongekumen

00:05:00.000 --> 00:05:02.680
fir vokhn far di bafrayung in BUCHENWALD

00:05:03.700 --> 00:05:06.700
un di mame iz umgekumen in TREBLINKA.

00:05:15.320 --> 00:05:18.000
koydem kol volt ikh gevolt dermanen

00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:21.500
az di ale bilder vos mir vayzn yetst

00:05:21.500 --> 00:05:24.180
fun far di milkhome

00:05:24.180 --> 00:05:27.140
dos ale bilder hob ikh gekrign fun mishpokhe

00:05:27.140 --> 00:05:30.410
in Amerike, in Kanade un Brazil.

00:05:31.010 --> 00:05:34.467
fun di heym hob ikh keyn shum zakh nisht.

00:05:35.440 --> 00:05:37.310
dos iz mayn muter

00:05:37.340 --> 00:05:39.650
halt mayn klenern bruder oyf di hant

00:05:39.650 --> 00:05:42.130
mayn klenstn, mayn yingstn bruder

00:05:42.130 --> 00:05:43.710
un

00:05:43.710 --> 00:05:45.910
fun di linke zayt iz mayn zeyde

00:05:47.420 --> 00:05:49.960
di mame's, Meyer TEITELBAUM

00:05:49.960 --> 00:05:51.850
un

00:05:51.850 --> 00:05:56.180
di bobe Nekhe. zi iz umge- zi iz geshtorbn a tsayt far di krig.

00:05:56.180 --> 00:05:59.430
mit di rekht, in di linke zayt iz mayns a

00:05:59.430 --> 00:06:02.640
a kuzinke, dem mame's bruder's a tokhter.

00:06:02.640 --> 00:06:05.570
zi lebt, un zi iz in RIO DE JANEIRO.

00:06:07.350 --> 00:06:09.558
der zeyde iz umgekumen

00:06:09.558 --> 00:06:13.025
genoy veys ikh nisht, ober ikh shtel mikh for az me hot im dershosn in Apt

00:06:13.025 --> 00:06:16.220
vayl ikh gloyb nisht az er hot gekent geyn tsu di ban

00:06:16.220 --> 00:06:18.896
vu me hot oyfgelodn di mentshn nokh TREBLINKA

00:06:18.896 --> 00:06:21.311
vayl er hot afile ni- fun di shtub nisht gekent aroysgeyn.

00:06:21.311 --> 00:06:23.220
azoy ikh ken zogn mit zikherkeyt

00:06:23.220 --> 00:06:27.506
az m'hot im dershosn bald in di shtub oyfn UNK plats.

00:06:32.752 --> 00:06:34.635
dos iz a bild

00:06:34.635 --> 00:06:39.869
vos iz gemakht gevorn a shtik far di milkhome. ikh gedenk nisht genoy vi alt ikh bin do gevezn.

00:06:39.869 --> 00:06:42.389
dos bin ikh di rekhte zayt.

00:06:42.389 --> 00:06:47.090
in di linke zayt vos shteyt iz mayn shvester

00:06:47.090 --> 00:06:49.129
Feyge

00:06:49.129 --> 00:06:53.246
un mayn klenerer bruder fornt, Moyshe.

00:06:53.466 --> 00:06:56.752
fun di zayt shteyt mayn tatn's a khaver's a zun.

00:06:56.882 --> 00:07:01.064
er iz punkt gevezn demolt bay undz, un zey hobn z- mir hobn zikh tsuzamen fotografirt.

00:07:00.591 --> 00:07:02.823
vos iz geshen? vos iz geshen mit zey ale?

00:07:01.895 --> 00:07:06.518
mit di, mit di, mit di sh- dem klenern bruder mit di shvester

00:07:06.518 --> 00:07:09.869
zenen geganen ⟨mit⟩ nokh TREBLINKA, veys ikh.

00:07:12.492 --> 00:07:15.466
dos iz mayn foter, Itsik Sherman.

00:07:15.466 --> 00:07:20.623
dos iz oykhet genumen gevorn mit, mit etlekhe zibetsik yor tsurik.

00:07:20.623 --> 00:07:22.766
finef zeks un zibetsik, efsher nokh mer.

00:07:22.766 --> 00:07:25.363
ikh denk az do iz er gevezn als khosn.

00:07:25.363 --> 00:07:30.428
er iz umgekumen fir vokhn far di bafrayung in BUCHENWALD.

00:07:34.272 --> 00:07:37.675
in di linke zayt iz mayn mamen

00:07:37.675 --> 00:07:39.986
Khaye, fun di heym TEITELBAUM

00:07:39.986 --> 00:07:42.649
velekhe iz umgekumen in TREBLINKA

00:07:42.649 --> 00:07:45.259
zitsedik iz irs a khaverte.

00:07:45.259 --> 00:07:48.441
zi ⟨iz,⟩ lebt nokh haynt, Khane Vek heyst zi.

00:07:48.441 --> 00:07:52.337
un zi, zi iz yetst, denk ikh, eyn un nayntsik yor.

00:07:56.155 --> 00:08:00.934
dos iz a bild f- mayn tate mit di mame in di mit.

00:08:00.934 --> 00:08:05.570
un di mame's a khaverte vos hobn- m'hot gezen frier oyf a bild, Khane Vek

00:08:05.570 --> 00:08:08.713
di eyntsike fun dem bild vos zi lebt.

00:08:09.428 --> 00:08:11.206
di ale andere

00:08:11.206 --> 00:08:13.739
der eyner in di mit iz der fun

00:08:13.739 --> 00:08:17.583
iz mayns a feter vos er iz geshtorbn mit a fuftsn yor tsurik in Kanade.

00:08:17.583 --> 00:08:21.479
ale iberike zenen, zenen farnikhtet gevorn.

00:08:26.155 --> 00:08:28.869
do bin ikh mit mayn froy

00:08:28.869 --> 00:08:31.531
eyder ikh bin geforn nokh Amerike.

00:08:31.531 --> 00:08:35.947
zi iz, gevezn krank, hot gemuzt tsurikforn oyf di Shveyts

00:08:35.947 --> 00:08:38.557
un dos bild iz gemakht gevorn

00:08:38.557 --> 00:08:42.883
ikh denk az in nayntsn eyn un fuftsik, in anfang nayntsn eyn un fuftsik.

00:08:43.220 --> 00:08:46.220
mayn froy hot geheysn Khane, fun di heym Kupfer.

00:08:50.493 --> 00:08:54.467
dos iz, a bild fun mayn mishpokhe.

00:08:54.467 --> 00:08:58.688
shteyedik bin ikh. in di mit iz mayn froy Khane

00:08:58.740 --> 00:09:00.649
mit mayne tsvey tekhters.

00:09:00.649 --> 00:09:02.506
fun di rekhte zayt SARA

00:09:02.506 --> 00:09:04.259
un di linke zayt TSIPORA.

00:09:04.259 --> 00:09:07.285
dos bild iz gemakht gevorn mistame mit a

00:09:08.467 --> 00:09:10.714
zibn un tsvantsik yor tsurik.

00:09:13.882 --> 00:09:18.765
dos iz mayn froy, ikh, oyb ikh de- gedenk iz dos dos letste bild.

00:09:18.765 --> 00:09:21.791
vos mayn froy iz nifter gevorn in nayntsn zibn un akhtsik

00:09:21.791 --> 00:09:24.376
fun a krankeyt, a lungen krankeyt

00:09:24.376 --> 00:09:27.402
vos hot zikh getsoygn zayt di bafrayung, zayt di milkhome.

00:09:27.402 --> 00:09:29.363
vos zi hot gekrign d- in di lagern.

00:09:29.363 --> 00:09:31.103
un d- f-

00:09:31.103 --> 00:09:34.817
in elter fun zekhtsik yor iz zi geshtorbn.

00:09:37.557 --> 00:09:40.505
dos iz a bild fun mayne tekhter

00:09:41.622 --> 00:09:44.233
di linke zayt di eltere SARA

00:09:44.233 --> 00:09:46.025
velekhe hot dray kinder

00:09:46.025 --> 00:09:49.557
tsvey meydlekh un a bokher.

00:09:49.557 --> 00:09:53.311
di, in di rekhte tsayt iz di yingere, TSIPORA

00:09:53.311 --> 00:09:56.259
velekhe voynt oyfn GOLAN, RAMAT HAGOLAN

00:09:56.259 --> 00:09:58.155
un hot finef kinder.

00:09:58.155 --> 00:10:00.909
tsvey yinglekh un dray meydlekh.

00:10:03.233 --> 00:10:05.895
 dos iz a bild.

00:10:05.895 --> 00:10:08.245
fun Poyln.

00:10:09.102 --> 00:10:13.440
mit finef yor tsurik zenen mir gevezn oyf a bazukh in undzer shtetl

00:10:13.440 --> 00:10:15.518
un dos iz dos hoyz

00:10:15.518 --> 00:10:19.324
vu ikh bin geshlofn bay i- mayn zeydn's

00:10:19.324 --> 00:10:20.999
s'iz a tsimer un a halb, eygntlekh.

00:10:21.752 --> 00:10:24.544
un dortn bin ikh geshlofn bay dem, dem zeydn.

00:10:24.544 --> 00:10:28.427
undzer hoyz vu ikh hob gevoynt iz in gantsn

00:10:28.427 --> 00:10:32.454
nishto. s'ekzistirt nisht. s'iz ⟨geven⟩ in gantsn a naye gegnt oysgeboyt.

00:10:32.454 --> 00:10:33.882
ober dos hoyz

00:10:33.882 --> 00:10:36.597
iz geblibn. ikh bin gevezn zeyer

00:10:36.597 --> 00:10:40.493
iberrasht tsu zen dos, az se ekzistirt nokh dos.

00:10:43.324 --> 00:10:45.038
dos iz a bukh

00:10:45.584 --> 00:10:48.856
vos Apter hobn ongeshribn

00:10:48.856 --> 00:10:51.700
vos yeder eyner hot gedenkt fun undzer shtot.

00:10:51.700 --> 00:10:53.181
mit

00:10:53.181 --> 00:10:57.038
der zikorn iz nokh gevezn a bisl frisher vi zi iz yetst, ober dos bukh hot shoyn ge-

00:10:57.038 --> 00:11:00.311
iz gemakht gevorn mit umgefer etlekhe draysik yor tsurik.

00:11:00.311 --> 00:11:05.168
un do in dem bukh gefi- gefinen zikh gesheenishn fun lager

00:11:05.168 --> 00:11:06.844
vos yeder eyner hot gedenkt

00:11:06.844 --> 00:11:08.493
fun di

00:11:08.493 --> 00:11:11.194
fun Apter geto, vos hot pasirt in geto

00:11:11.194 --> 00:11:14.116
zakhn vos yeder eyner hot gedenkt epes tsu dertseyln.

00:11:17.857 --> 00:11:20.480
do iz a shtik mape fun Poyln

00:11:20.480 --> 00:11:22.947
fun a shtikl Poyln, di gegnt

00:11:22.947 --> 00:11:26.012
vu undzer shtetl hot zikh gefinen, OPATOW.

00:11:26.012 --> 00:11:29.142
s'iz a- arumgetseykhnt mit royt.

00:11:31.765 --> 00:11:35.272
dos iz, vos UNK a mol ongerufn CONGRESS Poyln.
